`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Poofout
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax: `` 

 * poofout <message>

 The standard messages when leaving by goto is 'leaves in a swirling mist'. 
You can replace this message with a message of your own choosing using the
poofout command.  This messages must include your name somewhere in the string.


 Poofout only shows to characters who can see you.  To change the message seen
when arriving, use Poofin.

`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
